覆盖：
类 Throwable 中的 getMessage
返回：
the message. If an explicit error message has been assigned to the exception, this one is returned. If not, and there is an underlying exception (the cause), then the result of invoking Throwable.toString() on that object is returned. Otherwise, null is returned.
